lead_paragraph: A.J. Hammons scored 19 points to lead five Purdue players in double figures, and the 20th-ranked Boilermakers held on for an 83-79 victory over No. 10 Maryland on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Hammons Leads No. 20 Purdue Over No. 10 Maryland, 83-79
